## React Remix 


- Remix is an amazing React framework that vastly simplifies the process of building fullstack React web apps.

- A React fremwork that simplifies the creation of fullstack web apps
- Server-side rendered components $ enriched with backend logic

- Always server-side rendered
- No static site generations build-time pre-rendering
- Always requires host that supports server-side code execution

